LOCUS       Ptac                      55 bp    DNA              UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  Ptac is a synthetic sigma70 promoter combining the trp -35 with the
            lacUV5 -10 and operator, giving a strong, LacI/IPTG-inducible
            promoter for E. coli expression..
